112
00:07:36,295 --> 00:07:38,262
Werewolves? Come on, guys.

113
00:07:38,263 --> 00:07:40,965
What do I tell every reporter
on their first day of work?

114
00:07:40,966 --> 00:07:42,301
Don't start with the headline.

115
00:07:42,302 --> 00:07:43,901
Start with the facts.

116
00:07:43,902 --> 00:07:45,302
Which is why we're starting
with these facts...

117
00:07:45,303 --> 00:07:46,739
That there are people with

118
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:48,873
a really inappropriate
amount of body hair.

119
00:07:48,874 --> 00:07:50,108
Mm-hmm.

120
00:07:50,109 --> 00:07:51,808
They're also the symptoms
of hypertrichosis,

121
00:07:51,809 --> 00:07:52,978
a congenital condition

122
00:07:52,979 --> 00:07:55,313
that causes uncontrollable
hair growth.

123
00:07:55,314 --> 00:07:57,216
It's the same thing
that brought us...

124
00:07:57,217 --> 00:07:59,417
Julia Pastrana,

125
00:07:59,418 --> 00:08:01,119
the "Werewolf woman."

126
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,254
Been doing this a long time,

127
00:08:02,255 --> 00:08:03,921
and one of the
things I've learned

128
00:08:03,922 --> 00:08:07,659
is that the first answer
might not be the right one.

129
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:10,261
But it could be the answer
to selling more magazines.

130
00:08:10,262 --> 00:08:12,164
People dig a little
mystery, Hank...

131
00:08:12,165 --> 00:08:14,298
