reach-around...

132
00:08:14,299 --> 00:08:17,969
Things like spontaneous
combustion in Budapest.

133
00:08:17,970 --> 00:08:20,338
Or... Or skunk apes in Arkansas.

134
00:08:20,339 --> 00:08:22,141
I swear, you put one of
these on the cover...

135
00:08:22,142 --> 00:08:23,641
No, you know what?

136
00:08:23,642 --> 00:08:26,644
