with Laila for the weekend.

140
00:08:31,149 --> 00:08:33,185
Yeah, and we'll stay in one
room to keep costs down.

141
00:08:33,186 --> 00:08:34,218
No, we won't.

142
00:08:34,219 --> 00:08:35,721
What would make
Laila and I happiest

143
