152
00:09:09,188 --> 00:09:11,089
Laila?

153
00:09:11,090 --> 00:09:13,191
- They're trying to get in.
- Hold on. Talk to me.

154
00:09:13,192 --> 00:09:15,127
Call the police.
Honey, call the police!

