00:09:15,128 --> 00:09:16,983
Hey, Arron, call the
police. Don't ask.

156
00:09:16,984 --> 00:09:18,917
Just get 'em to Laila's shop now!

157
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,738
Okay, listen, I'm on
my way. Okay?

158
00:09:20,738 --> 00:09:21,595
You hear me?

159
00:09:22,101 --> 00:09:23,202
They're breaking in.

160
00:09:23,203 --> 00:09:25,270
Laila, what's going on?

161
00:09:25,271 --> 00:09:27,638
I've gotta fight 'em. There's
nothing else I can do.

162
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:29,409
No, no, do not fight them! Okay?
