incident on Bedford Avenue.

205
00:12:06,162 --> 00:12:07,495
FBI?

206
00:12:07,496 --> 00:12:09,030
We would've called
first, but we...

207
00:12:09,031 --> 00:12:11,733
No, no, no. It... It's fine.
Please, come in.

208
00:12:13,803 --> 00:12:17,939
No, I grabbed these because
I figured the could help.

209
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:21,009
