228
00:13:07,623 --> 00:13:09,924
Oh, God.

229
00:13:11,494 --> 00:13:13,528
Laila.

230
00:13:21,003 --> 00:13:22,637
Who is he?

231
00:13:22,638 --> 00:13:24,973
Name "White Vincent"
mean anything to you?

232
00:13:24,974 --> 00:13:26,508
No.

233
00:13:26,509 --> 00:13:28,210
He started out as
French Foreign Legion,

234
00:13:28,211 --> 00:13:30,612
