mercenary in the world.

235
00:13:30,613 --> 00:13:32,479
He's on every no-fly
list that we've got.

236
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,716
The fact that he's
operating on U.S. soil

237
00:13:33,717 --> 00:13:35,683
is obviously a problem.

238
00:13:35,684 --> 00:13:38,186
What would a guy like that
be doing taking my wife?

239
00:13:38,187 --> 00:13:40,755
Actually, that was gonna
be my question to you.

240
00:13:40,756 --> 00:13:41,922
W-What do you mean?

241
00:13:41,923 --> 00:13:43,090
Well, there's only so
much we can tell

242
00:13:43,091 --> 00:13:44,460
from credit card receipts,
travel records,

243
00:13:44,461 --> 00:13:46,561
- about a woman, and so I...
- A woman?

244
00:13:46,562 --> 00:13:47,763
You... You're talking
about Laila?

245
00:13:47,764 --> 00:13:49,898
She's the victim here.

246
00:13:49,899 --> 00:13:51,200
Well, that's certainly
how it would appear,

247
00:13:51,201 --> 00:13:53,735
but part of my job is to
look beyond appearances.

248
00:13:53,736 --> 00:13:56,237
I believe you do the same
thing at your magazine.

249
00:13:56,238 --> 00:13:58,238
So we were wondering if you
had any other information

250
00:13:58,239 --> 00:14:00,109
that might help us conduct
our investigation.

251
00:14:00,110 --> 00:14:01,876
Investigating who?

252
00:14:01,877 --> 00:14:03,578
My wife is not a terrorist.

253
00:14:03,579 --> 00:14:04,879
