254
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:06,046
And yet she's been kidnapped

255
00:14:06,047 --> 00:14:07,714
by one of the world's
most dangerous men.

256
00:14:07,715 --> 00:14:08,884
You don't find that odd?

257
00:14:10,186 --> 00:14:12,587
You know, you had me
when you came in here

